Tweet:
Unity in diversity is a promise we made when we made India into a Republic. 

Now, no Shah, Sultan or Samrat should renege on that promise. 

We respect all languages. 

Do not make an inclusive India into an exclusive one.
#HindiIsNotNationalLanguage
